the Intuitive iQ Global Intelligence Network at his website IntuitiveiQ.com. The website hosts videos and other important information about these innovators, discussion groups, and other social network qualities that enable all users to create their own pages in the network to promote themselves to and interact with the Intuitive iQ Global Community. The centerpiece of this amazing website is a unique Webseries that Mike created as well. On the Webseries he will interview all of these innovators in a LIVE interactive format, where the audience is able to ask questions and offer insights to meet the Guests and be a part of the discussions. \n\nMike is now preparing to Produce & Host this Webseries. For a preview, watch the Intuitive iQ video.',NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL),
