	(492,'Danny','Montero','montero@socialpicnik.com',NULL,NULL,'2012-05-24 21:28:11','a5a25c2a506d4601dd8817325d15dfac','https://s3.amazonaws.com/cf_stage/user/profile/492.jpg?701875',1,2930505,NULL,'',NULL,1,'Who am I? Why Social Picnik?\r\n\r\n\r\nWhat do you want to be when you grow up?\r\n\r\nIf you ask me Ill laugh and tell you \"I’m not ever growing up, are you?\"\r\n\r\nI’ve learned that life is ever changing and limitless to the desires you hold within yourself. You create your destiny through faith and belief within. If you can think it, you can create it.\r\n\r\nAs you grow older you tend to get told the world is the way it is and your life is just to live your life inside that world. Try not to bash into the walls too much. Try to have a nice family life, have fun, go to college, save a little money.\r\nThat’s a very limited life. Life can be much broader once you discover one simple fact- everything around you that you call life, was made up by people that were no smarter than you. And you can change it, you can influence it, you can build your own things that other people can use.\r\nThe moment that you understand you can poke life and something will actually pop out the other side, that you can change it, you can mold it. That’s the moment your life will change.\r\n\r\nWe should all challenge ourselves to the beat of one simple quote.\r\n\r\n“Think Differently”\r\n\r\nThrough thinking differently I’ve found my life’s desire. To create bigger and better things for all of us now and in the future. To help the things we love today; evolve and change for the future. \r\n\r\nThis desire has brought me to a web start up that I feel can leave a pretty big mark on that thing we call the Internet. Help me to create something we both can share and be proud of. Be apart of something bigger, be a part of\r\n\r\nSocial Picnik.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n-Danny Montero\r\n  CEO & Founder\r\n',NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL),
