	(782,'marco','brambilla','marco.brambilla@hotmail.com',NULL,NULL,'2012-05-28 14:21:53','45501d7ffe84829632fb9e22f75a0bad','https://s3.amazonaws.com/cf_stage/user/profile/782.jpg?573884',1,0,NULL,'',NULL,1,'Wooib is a location-based social networking website for smartphones, tablets and desktops where users download a device specific application that enables them to take a photo or video at any venue and have that photo or video appear on the first interactive map of its kind.  Location is based on GPS hardware in the mobile device or network location provided by the application.  By allowing registered users, named the Wooiber Generation, to post an image at a venue, thus, “Leave Your Mark,” they can connect with friends and discover what is nearby.  \r\n\r\nWooib has positioned itself in the geo-social network market as both an end user application, as an advertising vehicle and as a franchiser to a team of franchisees.  As described above, users download a mobile device specific application and begin using the service by taking photographs and videos and upload them so that their location is pinpointed on an interactive map.  Wooibers are then engaged to see what is around them through banner ads, videos, and pins that suggests possible matches in interest.  Advertisers are strategically matched to Wooibers based on their location and demographic.',NULL,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL),
