	(880,'Jonathan','Govette','Jonathan@getreferralmd.com','referralMD, CEO',NULL,'2012-05-29 17:56:56','efc03c94ab0d977e2b452385dd6573ee','https://s3.amazonaws.com/cf_stage/user/profile/880.png?715889',1,2922110,NULL,'',NULL,1,'WHO IS JONATHAN GOVETTE?\n\nJonathan Govette is the founder of ReferralMD – a patient referral management application that is designed for any size organization, from a single practitioner to a large hospital. ReferralMD seeks to become the replacement for the fax machine and allow millions of doctors the ability to track referrals without digging through file cabinets or using excel.\n\nAs ReferralMD’s strategic leader, Jonathan is responsible for developing key relationships with healthcare organizations, online positioning, branding, product design, and team development.\n\n--------------------\n\nGETREFERRALMD.COM\n\nIn 2007, our founder, Jonathan Govette, saw the rise of 100’s of medical record software applications that managed patient records, prescriptions, scheduling etc, but none had an ability to easily communicate referrals without the headache and inaccuracies of paper faxing and triplicate forms.\n\nAfter many years of research and speaking with 100’s of doctors, we developed a web-based cloud application that exchanges referrals quickly and efficiently and can complement any medical records software. Our goal is to create the next standard (replacing the fax machine) for referrals and integrating our software into every major healthcare institution in the world.\n',1,NULL,0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL),
